com.ephesoft.dcma.gwt.core.shared.util

Class DTOUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ephesoft.dcma.gwt.core.shared.util.DTOUtil

  • public class DTOUtil
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides utility methods for creating the replicas of DTOs and list of DTOs.

    The DTOUtil class defines methods for making copies of KVExtractionDTO, RegexDTO and list of such DTOs.
